                <h2 class="section-title text-center wow fadeInDown">About Pernankila</h2>
                <p class="text-center text-justify justified wow fadeInDown"><b>Pernankila</b> is a  village near Hiriadka, located in the district of <b>Udupi</b> in Karnataka. This village is blessed by divine blessings and is considered to be filled with divine power. The divine abode of <b>Lord Shri Mahalingeshwara</b> and <b>Shri Mahaganapathi</b> is situated in here which is about 20 km southeast of Udupi. The Ganapathi here is called as <b><i>Udbava Ganapati</i></b> as it is believed to have come from earth by itself. People believe that he removes obstacles from one's life. </p>
